{
  "stem": "8370.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, as I told you, I was working first in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I catched typhoid or black fever, we call it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And afterwards, I was still in the hospital for a couple of weeks, recovering.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had a, I would say, personality clash with the chief doctor in this hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he kicked me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to a commander of a road builder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was building roads.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, till now, the roads are experienced-- the roads are in good condition.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a good job done, even when I, after the war, 20 years after the war, I arrived by [? my ?] car.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was driving on the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was proud of my job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyhow, sorry to say that they have been the roads gaining to the, going to the crematoriums, the main roads.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyhow, well, and working on the roads, I saw, of course, the hundred of thousand, if not millions, of people brought to the camp and sent to, to gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were different, from all around the world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, I saw many time the selection of the [? ramp-- ?] done by Mengele and other doctors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was left, right, left, right, left, right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To the one side, they were, they were sending people young, strong, or healthy-looking, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Except when it was a young, healthy woman, and had a child with her, she was sent to the gas chamber together with the child.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If she gave her child to a older woman, she had a chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I was proud of the Polish girl, Polish mother, Jewish mother, who went with their children, knowing what's going on to the right, to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
